name: BDPMQ 1
notes: Chron uses 2 radiocarbon dates, 2 adjusted dates, and the surface (0 BP). The dates at 10.5 and 35.5 cm were chosen to be the C14 date minus 2 SD, which makes them all monotonic and which agrees with sediment stratigraphy.
